{{> layout/header-admin}}
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/venue-save.css">

<main class="cc-main">
    <div class="cc-container">

        <section class="cc-card admin-venue-save-card">

            <div class="admin-venue-save-head">
                <p class="admin-venue-eyebrow">관리자 메뉴</p>

                <h1 class="admin-venue-title">공연장 등록</h1>

                <p class="admin-venue-desc">
                    콘서트 예매에 사용할 공연장 정보를 입력해 주세요.
                </p>
            </div>

            <form class="admin-venue-form" action="/admin/venues/save" method="post">
                {{#_csrf}}
                    <input type="hidden" name="{{parameterName}}" value="{{token}}">
                {{/_csrf}}

                <div class="admin-venue-form-grid">

                    <div class="cc-field admin-venue-field">
                        <label for="name">공연장명</label>
                        <input
                                id="name"
                                class="cc-input"
                                type="text"
                                name="name"
                                placeholder="예: KSPO DOME"
                                required>
                    </div>

                    <div class="cc-field admin-venue-field">
                        <label for="totalCapacity">총 수용 인원</label>
                        <input
                                id="totalCapacity"
                                class="cc-input"
                                type="number"
                                name="totalCapacity"
                                placeholder="예: 15000"
                                min="1"
                                required>
                    </div>

                    <div class="cc-field admin-venue-field admin-venue-field--full">
                        <label for="address">주소</label>
                        <input
                                id="address"
                                class="cc-input"
                                type="text"
                                name="address"
                                placeholder="예: 서울특별시 송파구 올림픽로 424"
                                required>
                    </div>

                </div>

                <div class="admin-venue-help">
                    <span>안내</span>
                    등록한 공연장은 콘서트 등록 시 공연장 선택 목록에 사용됩니다.
                </div>

                <div class="admin-venue-form-actions">
                    <a class="cc-btn cc-btn--outline admin-venue-cancel-btn" href="/admin/venues">
                        목록으로
                    </a>

                    <button class="cc-btn cc-btn--primary admin-venue-submit-btn" type="submit">
                        공연장 등록
                    </button>
                </div>
            </form>

        </section>

    </div>
</main>

{{> layout/footer}}